BEHAVIOUR DRIVEN TESTING

Login

An existing user can login to the application and be passed on to the high score screen

A new user can sign up for an account and be passed through to the high score screen.


High Scores

The page should request and interpret a list of 'best' scores from the database for All Users
The page should request and interpret a list of 'best' scores for this user.
The page should request and interpret the RANK of this user's best score.

The page should render the two lists - highest score to the top and display the rank of this user.


Help

The page should provide game play directions.


